
========================================================
  GLIA Live — Linux with a built-in AI terminal assistant
========================================================

Your AI assistant is called  my_pc

  my_pc <request>        proposes a shell command (Enter = run)
  my_pc -d <question>    plain-text answer, no command
  glia-hardware          shows the recommended AI model for this machine

First step (needs network):

  ollama pull qwen3:4b   # or the model suggested by glia-hardware

Dangerous commands always require typing YES.
Project: https://github.com/micheleperani76/GLIA

